<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<!DOCTYPE plist PUBLIC "-//Apple//DTD PLIST 1.0//EN" "http://www.apple.com/DTDs/PropertyList-1.0.dtd">
<plist version="1.0">
<!--
  Privacy manifest for the Codescribe app bundle. Wired into the Codescribe
  target via macos/project.yml (resources build phase), so xcodebuild copies it
  to Codescribe.app/Contents/Resources/PrivacyInfo.xcprivacy and codesign
  covers it. Materialized from scripts/PrivacyInfo.xcprivacy.template; see
  docs/APP_STORE_READINESS.md for the full rationale and Apple citations.

  Required-reason API usage (verified against the code, not assumed):
    std::fs metadata().modified() in core/state/history.rs, core/hf_cache.rs,
    core/attachment.rs and core/pipeline/stream_postprocess.rs reads file
    modification times of files inside the app's own directories ->
    NSPrivacyAccessedAPICategoryFileTimestamp, reason C617.1 ("access file
    metadata ... within the app container, app group container, or the app's
    CloudKit container"). No UserDefaults/@AppStorage usage exists in the
    Swift layer, so no UserDefaults category is declared.

  Data collection, honestly:
    - Microphone audio is transcribed ON-DEVICE (embedded Whisper) and never
      leaves the machine, so audio is not "collected" in Apple's sense
      (no off-device transmission). The Audio Data nutrition label is an App
      Store Connect questionnaire item, separate from this file.
    - In the AI modes ONLY (formatting / assistive / selection), transcribed
      text and user-provided context are sent to the user-configured LLM
      provider (e.g. OpenAI, Anthropic) to service the request. That is
      user-generated content leaving the device -> declared below as
      OtherUserContent, purpose App Functionality, not linked to identity,
      not used for tracking.

  Created by Vetcoders (c)2026
-->
<dict>
    <!-- This app does not track users across apps/websites owned by others. -->
    <key>NSPrivacyTracking</key>
    <false/>

    <key>NSPrivacyTrackingDomains</key>
    <array/>

    <key>NSPrivacyCollectedDataTypes</key>
    <array>
        <dict>
            <!-- Transcript/context text sent to the configured LLM provider,
                 only when the user invokes an AI mode. -->
            <key>NSPrivacyCollectedDataType</key>
            <string>NSPrivacyCollectedDataTypeOtherUserContent</string>
            <key>NSPrivacyCollectedDataTypeLinked</key>
            <false/>
            <key>NSPrivacyCollectedDataTypeTracking</key>
            <false/>
            <key>NSPrivacyCollectedDataTypePurposes</key>
            <array>
                <string>NSPrivacyCollectedDataTypePurposeAppFunctionality</string>
            </array>
        </dict>
    </array>

    <!-- Required-reason API declarations (mandatory since 2024-05-01). -->
    <key>NSPrivacyAccessedAPITypes</key>
    <array>
        <dict>
            <key>NSPrivacyAccessedAPIType</key>
            <string>NSPrivacyAccessedAPICategoryFileTimestamp</string>
            <key>NSPrivacyAccessedAPITypeReasons</key>
            <array>
                <!-- C617.1: access file metadata within the app's own containers. -->
                <string>C617.1</string>
            </array>
        </dict>
    </array>
</dict>
</plist>
